def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if x = 0 then 0 else x / 2 ^ (x.trailingZeroes)

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  Nat.find_greatest (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) x

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if x = 0 then 0 else Finset.max' (Finset.filter Nat.Odd (Finset.divisors x)) ⟨1, by simp⟩

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  x.div2 ^ x.bodd * (x / x.div2 ^ x.bodd)

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  x / (2 ^ (Nat.findGreatest (fun k => 2 ^ k ∣ x) (x.bitLength - 1)))

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  x.div2 ^ x.bodd * (if x.bodd then 1 else 2)

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  x / (2 ^ x.twos)

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if x = 0 then 0 else x / (2 ^ x.trailingZeroes)

def greatestOddDivisor (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  Nat.factorization x 1
